   [$ (^L. Col. Lilb.^) $] I thank you Sir, but under your favour    #
thus, your
indictment is extream long, and of aboundance of particulars, it is
impossible that my memory, or of any one mans in (^England^) , can 
contain it, or carry it in our heads, and therefore that I may make my
